---
title: 'Convenient 24/7 Payments with HG&E's NEW Bilingual Drive Thru Kiosk'
date: 2021-11-08T17:01:34+07:00
layout: post
---
<!-- Holyoke, MA -->
HG&E is excited to announce a new self-service payment kiosk which is located behind the main office! With a simple click, the kiosk will offer detailed instructions in both Spanish and English.

<h2>Payment Kiosk Tips:<h2>

● Pay anytime by cash, check, or credit card.

● Bring your account number to make a payment

● After an initial payment using the kiosk, the system will conveniently store your account information for next time.

● If you have any questions while you are using the kiosk, contact Customer Service by utilizing the call button on the left hand side of the kiosk (during business hours).

